property.name: SMOOTH
property.shortdesc: The point is a smooth point, it has two direction lines which are parallel.

property.name: CORNER
property.shortdesc: The point is a corner point, it has either one direction line, or two independent direction lines.

property.name: PLAIN
property.shortdesc: The point is a plain point, it has no direction lines.

property.name: SYMMETRICAL
property.shortdesc: A special type of smooth point with two direction lines of equal length.
